      • loadAll

        public static void loadAll()

      • generateTexture

        private static void generateTexture(java.lang.String mask,
                                    java.lang.String overlay,
                                    java.lang.String base,
                                    java.lang.String suffix)
        Composes a texture out of a solid color alpha mask, an upper layer overlay that is laid on top of a base texture. In this particular use-case, a solid terrain texture is clipped with a mask and then a specific semi-transparent edge overlay is laid on top.

      • unloadAll

        public static void unloadAll()
        Disposes of all textures that were loaded. Should be called on application exit.

      • getProgress

        public static float getProgress()
        Returns the progress of the current loading task progressMessage. Percentage range 0-100. Name of the task can be accessed via getMessage().
